Title: Outlook Weekend: Am I Baby Paul?
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/w3cswt5t
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 27 May 2018
A kidnapped baby, an abandoned child and a web of secrets that spanned over 40 years. Paul Fronczak grew up knowing his past was confusing, but it was only decades later that he would begin to untangle these mysteries and get the answers he was searching for about his true identity. Image: shadow of a woman pushing a pram Credit: AlexLinch/iStock/Getty Images Plus Presenter: Harry Graham Show less